<theme id="thm224">
<titleabbrev>Lesson %d</titleabbrev>
<title>Note tied to four 16th notes</title>
<tocimage>img224.png</tocimage>

<para>In this lesson the next patterns are introduced:</para>

<score>
    <music>
    (score (vers 1.6)
      (instrument
        (musicData
        (time 2 4 noVisible)
        (n * q l)(n * s g+)(n * s)(n * s)(n * s g-)(barline double)
        (n * e g+)(n * e l g-)(n * s g+)(n * s)(n * s)(n * s g-)(barline end)
    )))
    </music>
</score>

<part>
<title>Listen and take notice of the differences</title>

<score>
    <control_play />
    <control_measures />
    <music>
    (score (vers 1.6)
      (instrument
        (musicData
        (clef G)(key C)(time 2 4)
        (n a4 q l)(n a4 s g+)(n a4 s)(n a4 s)(n a4 s g-)(barline)
        (n a4 e g+)(n a4 e l g-)(n a4 s g+)(n a4 s)(n a4 s)(n a4 s g-)(barline end)
    )))
    </music>
</score>
</part>

